Stacy Dorning https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stacy_Dorning 0 Stacy Dorning (born 11 May 1958 in London) is an English actress, best known for appearing in the second series of The Adventures of Black Beauty (1973–74). She also appeared in Just William (1977–78) and Keep It in the Family (1980–83). She is the elder daughter of actors Robert Dorning and Honor Shepherd, and older sister of actress Kate Dorning.
